TuxChan - A 4chan desktop client
===============================================================================

TuxChan is a desktop client for 4chan. 4chan is described as:

  4chan is a simple image-based bulletin board where anyone can post comments
  and share images.
                -- from http://4chan.org

With this application you can follow images stream from your preferred
channels, and be notified about new contents in a more efficient way than the
web interface.

TuxChan homepage is available at: http://tuxchan.barberaware.org/

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TuxChan depends on:

  - libgio >= 2.20.3
  - libgtk2 >= 2.10.0
  - Clutter >= 1.0.0
  - libsoup >= 2.26.2
  - libmagic

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./configure
make
sudo make install

